{"version":1,"entries":{"person_234924_translations":{"at":1772689424038,"data":{"id":234924,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Jessica Alice Cave Lloyd (born May 5, 1987) is an English actress, comedian and cartoonist, known for her role as Lavender Brown in the Harry Potter film series and for her shows in London and at the Edinburgh Fringe. She has also published a book of cartoon doodles called Love Sick, some of the designs in which have appeared on greeting cards. A comedic play based on her life and relationships, Sunrise, was first performed in 2019. Cave's first novel, Sunset, was published in 2021.","name":"Jessie Cave","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Jessie Cave est une actrice et caricaturiste britannique.\n\nElle est née à Londres en Angleterre le 5 mai 1987. Son père travaillait comme médecin généraliste, elle a trois frères et une sœur.\n\nC'est une ancienne joueuse de tennis nationale. Après des cours d'illustration et d'animation à l'Université Kingston de Londres et divers petits boulots en coulisses dans quelques théâtres, Jessie Cave décide de s'orienter vers la comédie. Après un petit rôle dans le téléfilm Summerhill, elle est admise à la Oxford School of Drama. Elle choisit toutefois de différer son entrée dans cette prestigieuse école afin de pouvoir participer au tournage de Harry Potter et le Prince de sang-mêlé, dans lequel elle campe Lavande Brown, l'amoureuse haute en couleurs de Ron Weasley.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"杰西卡·爱丽丝·凯夫·劳埃德（Jessica Alice Cave Lloyd，1987 年 5 月 5 日出生）是一位英国女演员、喜剧演员和漫画家，因在《哈利波特》系列电影中饰演薰衣草布朗以及在伦敦和爱丁堡艺穗节的表演而闻名。她还出版了一本名为《Love Sick》的卡通涂鸦书，其中一些设计出现在贺卡上。根据她的生活和人际关系改编的喜剧《日出》于 2019 年首次上演。凯夫的第一部小说《日落》于 2021 年出版。","name":"杰西卡·凯夫","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"傑西卡·愛麗絲·凱夫·勞埃德（Jessica Alice Cave Lloyd，1987 年 5 月 5 日出生）是一位英國女演員、喜劇演員和漫畫家，因在《哈利波特》系列電影中飾演薰衣草布朗以及在倫敦和愛丁堡藝穗節的表演而聞名。她還出版了一本名為《Love Sick》的卡通塗鴉書，其中一些設計出現在賀卡上。根據她的生活和人際關係改編的喜劇《日出》於 2019 年首次上演。凱夫的第一部小説《日落》於 2021 年出版。","name":"傑西卡·凱夫","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Джесси Кейв","primary":false}}]}},"tv_295117_credits":{"at":1772689426852,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1926550,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Huang Junjie","original_name":"黄俊捷","popularity":1.2738,"profile_path":"/fBiEiyYdDzrhyXqL8n9BNryn12y.jpg","character":"Yun Zhan / Cang Lin","credit_id":"68641727ae1974c5611f80a3","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":2459066,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Wu Jiayi","original_name":"吳佳怡","popularity":1.7226,"profile_path":"/eVVguFgs2NNIOlRUgAYbCxb1R3h.jpg","character":"Feng Li","credit_id":"686417376f93f51dd91f806d","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":2318558,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Jing Yanjun","original_name":"景研竣","popularity":0.9858,"profile_path":"/pxYjuRTvAUepSXBm1GGiqhJ52rW.jpg","character":"Bai Yu","credit_id":"695e1996192a190b48f29018","order":2},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":4253468,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Dai Meng","original_name":"Dai Meng","popularity":0.2941,"profile_path":"/q00GI8CZL1UFjme5D8OSQChw8NS.jpg","character":"Meng Wu","credit_id":"695e19a98def770bc741599d","order":3},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":5923936,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Liu Yuyin","original_name":"刘雨银","popularity":0.1071,"profile_path":null,"character":"Xin Miao","credit_id":"695e1a16e3212bc3a5b5e336","order":4},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":3826613,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Shang Na","original_name":"尚娜","popularity":1.5073,"profile_path":"/ioUraH2AahGD8NfrpDmnSc8zExS.jpg","character":"Rao Jun","credit_id":"695e1