:{"id":3861806,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"Γεννημένη στις 12 Νοεμβρίου 1998, η Zheng Cheng Cheng είναι Κινέζα ηθοποιός και τραγουδίστρια. Το 2017, έκανε το ντεμπούτο της ως ηθοποιός στην τηλεοπτική σειρά \"K.O.3an Guo 2017\" ως Zen Mi. Τον Απρίλιο του 2018 συμμετείχε στο τηλεοπτικό βαριετέ σόου της Tencent \"Produce 101 China\" και τον Νοέμβριο του ίδιου έτους πρωταγωνίστησε στην τηλεοπτική σειρά \"Hi, I'm Saori\" ως Lan Tian.\n\nΕίναι μέλος των KOGIRLS, που έκανε το ντεμπούτο της τον Νοέμβριο του 2017, και των Hao Girls, που έκανε το ντεμπούτο της το 2018.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zheng Chengcheng","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zheng Cheng Cheng","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"郑丞丞","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"鄭丞丞","primary":false}}]}},"person_1128192_translations":{"at":1772689446635,"data":{"id":1128192,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Jessica Knappett is an actress and writer. In 2005 Jessica co-formed Lady Garden, a female comedy group, who performed to some acclaim at the Brighton and Edinburgh Fringe Festivals. She came to fame with her role as Neil's holiday girlfriend, Lisa, in The Inbetweeners Movie. In 2013 she created, wrote and starred in her own sitcom Drifters which ran for four series until 2016. She is married to Dan Crane, an American musician, writer and world champion professional air guitarist. They welcomed their first child, a daughter, in the summer of 2017.","name":"Jessica Knappett","primary":true}}]}},"movie_1318370_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1772689456853,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/izM86U07mPmPwpQzKhqj04gNaMc.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":27,"name":"Phim Kinh Dị"},{"id":28,"name":"Phim Hành Động"},{"id":53,"name":"Phim Gây Cấn"},{"id":80,"name":"Phim Hình Sự"}],"homepage":"","id":1318370,"imdb_id":"tt33022038","origin_country":["ID"],"original_language":"id","original_title":"Gundik","overview":"","popularity":2.3696,"poster_path":"/bi7e8dhSlHvi5AdrwJDMw0GqN1w.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":104948,"logo_path":"/9qhbSev7cS66drQCtPAi0On8a6D.png","name":"Umbara Brothers Film","origin_country":"ID"},{"id":234209,"logo_path":null,"name":"Makara Production","origin_country":""},{"id":99937,"logo_path":null,"name":"786 Production","origin_country":"ID"},{"id":188528,"logo_path":null,"name":"RUMPI Entertainment","origin_country":"ID"},{"id":235238,"logo_path":"/kfZd64gNwp6JAcUYXjQ8xAon4u4.png","name":"Role Entertainment","origin_country":"ID"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"ID","name":"Indonesia"}],"release_date":"2025-05-22","revenue":0,"runtime":112,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Indonesian","iso_639_1":"id","name":"Bahasa indonesia"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Gundik","video":false,"vote_average":5.4,"vote_count":4}},"person_5958274_translations":{"at":1772689456999,"data":{"id":5958274,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Triệu An","primary":true}}]}},"person_1753341_translations":{"at":1772689458491,"data":{"id":1753341,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Frankie Adams is a New Zealand actress and amateur boxer of Samoan heritage. She is 6 ft (1.8 m) tall.\n\nAdams' first role, aged 16, was that of Ula Levi in the soap opera Shortland Street. She has also had roles in the television series Wentworth and in the film 1000 Ropes.\n\nAs a boxer, Adams has participated in a Fight For Life charity boxing event","name":"Frankie Adams","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Frankie Adams es una actriz mejor conocida por sus papeles como Bobbie Draper en la serie de televisión de ciencia ficción The Expanse y como Ula Levi en la telenovela Shortland Street. Es una actriz y boxeadora amateur de Nueva Zelanda de herencia samoana. Mide 1.8 m de altura. El primer papel de Adams, de 16 años, fue el de Ula Levi en la telenovela Shortland Street. También ha tenido papeles en la serie de televisión Wentworth y en la película 1000 Ropes. Como boxeadora, Adams ha participado en un evento de boxeo de caridad Fight For Life","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"Frankie Adamsová je novozélandská herečka a amatérská boxerka samojského původu. Je vysoká 1,8 m.\n\nPrvní rolí Adamsové byla ve věku 16 let role Uly Leviové v telenovele Shortland Street. Měla také role v televizním seriálu Wentworth a ve filmu 1000 provazů.\n\nJako boxerka se Adamsová zúčastnila charitativní boxerské akce Fight For Life.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"弗兰基·亚当斯（Frankie Adams）是新西兰女演员和萨摩亚血统的业余拳击手。\n\n亚当斯的第一个角色是 16 岁时在肥皂剧《肖特兰街》中扮演的乌拉·列维。她还曾在电视连续剧《温特沃斯》和电影《1000 根绳索》中扮演角色。\n\n作为一名拳击手，亚当斯参加了“为生命而战”慈善拳击活动","name":"弗兰基·亚当斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"弗蘭基·亞當斯（Frankie Adams）是紐西蘭女演員和薩摩亞血統的業餘拳擊手。\n\n亞當斯的第一個角色是 16 歲時在肥皂劇《肖特蘭街》中扮演的烏拉·列維。她還曾在電視聯續劇《温特沃斯》和電影《1000 根繩索》中扮演角色。\n\n作為一名拳擊手，亞當斯參加了“為生命而戰”慈善拳擊活動","name":"弗蘭基·亞當斯","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"